(x_1+\cdots+x_n)^k=\sum_{\alpha,|\alpha|=k}\frac{|\alpha|!}{\alpha!}x^\alpha 
\alpha =(\alpha_1,\alpha_2,\cdots,\alpha_n)
|\alpha|=\alpha_1+\alpha_2+\cdots+\alpha_n
\alpha!=\alpha_1!\alpha_2!\cdots\alpha_n!
|\alpha|=k
